UnfoldU as a socially responsible organisation, has always taken fruitful and visionary decisions to achieve the main objective of "providing most economical digital education to the maximum number of students at their doorstep".

Now, to support the real talent of the society, UnfoldU as a leader in digital education, announces "UnfoldU Scholarship Programme (USP)". This Scholarship will be offered to the UnfoldU students only (Students who are currently enrolled with UnfoldU's "Personalised Learning System") on the basis of the Online UnfoldU Scholarship Exam to be conducted by UnfoldU.

Key Features of UnfoldU Scholarship Program are as under-

1. The amount of the scholarship will be equal to the total fee of the student for whole session starting from April 2021 to March 2022, or upto Rs.1 Lakh, whichever is lesser.
2. In case of equal marks, the open draw will be organised by UnfoldU.
3. One last date will be announced to give the Name of Student along with Student’s UnfoldU ID, to participate in UnfoldU Scholarship Programme.
4. The students will be allowed to participate in UnfoldU Scholarship Exam only after proper identity verification.
5. A nominal participation fee will be applicable for the students to participate in UnfoldU Scholarship Programme which will be announced before commencement of the Scholarship Exam.
6. Special Online Exam will be conducted in April/May 2021 for the students of the Session of 2020-21.
Example- The students who are studying in 10th in the Session 2020-21, will appear for 10th class UnfoldU Scholarship Exam in April/May 2021 to compete for UnfoldU Scholarship for 11th Class.
7. The questions in UnfoldU Scholarship Exam will be objective in nature and all the major subjects will be covered as per latest NCERT syllabus.
8. The maximum marks and other criteria of the scholarship exam will be decided before the commencement of UnfoldU Scholarship Exam.
9. The number of scholarships and categories of classes for the scholarship will be decided before the commencement of the UnfoldU Scholarship Exam.
The UnfoldU Scholarship Programme is going to be a real honour to the talented and deserving students of the society, and this step will definitely support and enhance the young minds who are the most valuable assets of our society.
UnfoldU reserves all the rights to change or upgrade any specifications or features of the UnfoldU Scholarship Programme.

The Personalized Learning System of UnfoldU is a visionary initiative of its Founder and Chairman Sh. Harish Kumar Bajaj to provide most advanced form of digital education to the students. Presently among the top 10 E-Learning Apps in India, UnfoldU is not just an App. It is a tool which offers several different interactive and interesting methods to the students which include- Learning via Engaging Mentor Videos, Conceptual Videos, Homework Help, Revision Facilities and MCQs Practice. UnfoldU's Self Study System includes more than 5000 Basic Conceptual Videos, more than 2.2 Lakhs Solved Questions, more than 65000 Quick Review Slides, more than 30000 Sub-Topic Videos, more than 33000 Objective Questions and many student useful features like Ask Your Doubt, Formula Book, Digital Notes and U-Live Test. The queries of the students are answered in the most effective way to enhance their understanding of the concepts. UnfoldU covers the syllabus of CBSE and other state boards as well where the students get to understand the concepts in both the languages English and Hindi. UnfoldU offers a student friendly App which carries the complete solution of all the needs and requirements of a student to have a thorough understanding of the study material.
